I braved the dreaded babelfish for this. And while I'm not getting much 
out of it it's worth looking up for the "person photo studio" button at 
the  bottom under "Index" There are pictures of Takasugi and Ryoma 
Sakamoto I hadn't seen before and a bunch of other guys whose 
babelfish-ese weird name translations I haven't come across before 
enough to hazard a guess as to who they are.

Luckily everyone's favorite Vice-chief "Manual Laborer Year Three" is 
included in the line up.
